org.jetel.graph.modelview

Interface MVGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MVGraphElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MVEngineGraph

    public interface MVGraph
extends MVGraphElement
    This is general model view to a transformation graph. This model view is used by MetadataPropagationResolver.
